{"tid":1881133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不斷問點光復香港？點保全香港文化？","createTime":"2020-02-15T10:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T01:47:26.000Z","uid":222541,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb9b84cea1121f22053998f73ff2633fa701c41","tid":1881133,"uid":222541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"先要知咩係香港文化先啦，段片太長，不了？較1.25/1.5倍囉<br />\n睇完會知保育香港文化個個都可以做到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YmnXr1_B-Hs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYmnXr1_B-Hs&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=b10df155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YmnXr1_B-Hs</a><br />\n<br />\n場運動點抗爭呀？要贏呀！中國電影不了？睇完你會問點解呢套戲冇被禁，同埋點解係中國電影教你點抗爭嘅？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL6g4QOGqMBY&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=3715dc62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L6g4QOGqMBY</a><br />\n<br />\n真心想香港好嘅，真係要花時間睇同思考，香港人已經冇乜本錢再做港豬，唔好再做政治bb，多d了解歷史同政治，願榮光歸香港。"},{"pid":"a8b6e45b200bc7630c985b6ae6c001b8335d232b","tid":1881133,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=779980c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"c2a76f4e83c92ce2b4625fd7d67abf285aeb3c68","tid":1881133,"uid":222541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT